WEBVTT

00:04:40.462 --> 00:04:41.549
Money!

00:04:42.668 --> 00:04:45.379
Money! Money is coming in!

00:04:45.504 --> 00:04:47.837
Money is coming from the top,
from the bottom!

00:04:47.971 --> 00:04:49.074
Only money!

00:04:50.087 --> 00:04:51.545
The money is colour,
the money is beauty!

00:04:51.670 --> 00:04:53.295
A man is nothing without money.

00:04:53.420 --> 00:04:58.795
Money, all over the place.
Money is raining.

00:05:00.587 --> 00:05:03.670
Soft money! What a money!

00:05:03.754 --> 00:05:05.712
Silky money! My money!
So much money.

00:05:05.795 --> 00:05:07.920
He is dreaming again.
- Money!

00:05:08.075 --> 00:05:10.427
Why are you tearing the mattress?
Come to your senses.

00:05:10.586 --> 00:05:12.837
What are you doing? Bring some water.

00:05:12.920 --> 00:05:15.761
Money is raining?
- What are you doing?

00:05:16.712 --> 00:05:18.212
Money!
- Come to your senses.

00:05:18.295 --> 00:05:21.254
Money!
- Come to your senses.

00:05:21.837 --> 00:05:24.420
The flood.

00:05:24.504 --> 00:05:26.004
Come to your senses.

00:05:31.040 --> 00:05:33.004
This is not money. It's just cotton.

00:05:33.271 --> 00:05:35.545
You have spoilt my lakhs of rupees.

00:05:35.781 --> 00:05:39.151
You already have lakhs of rupees.
How much more do you want?

00:05:39.281 --> 00:05:42.545
Crores.
I want to earn crores of rupees.

00:05:43.098 --> 00:05:46.605
You don't know what happens
to me when I see money.

00:05:46.897 --> 00:05:50.397
I feel ecstatic when I see money!

00:05:50.938 --> 00:05:53.206
My whole body starts to dance.

00:05:53.629 --> 00:05:57.036
I hear melodious music.

00:05:57.378 --> 00:05:59.943
Flowers blossom in my eyes.

00:06:00.097 --> 00:06:01.765
I can do anything for money.

00:06:01.995 --> 00:06:04.397
I can live, I can die.
I can sing. I can dance.

00:06:04.480 --> 00:06:05.966
Can you take a bath?
- What?

00:06:06.046 --> 00:06:08.288
Can you take a bath?
The priest is about to come.

00:06:08.368 --> 00:06:11.230
