is about to get some good news.

00:06:11.313 --> 00:06:13.980
The priest is about
to get some good news.

00:06:15.647 --> 00:06:18.688
Hail Lakshmi (Goddess of wealth).

00:06:18.803 --> 00:06:21.230
Hail Lakshmi.

00:06:22.239 --> 00:06:26.158
Mother Lakshmi, your love for the owl,
your ride, very much..

00:06:26.736 --> 00:06:28.980
I am your greatest devotee.

00:06:29.216 --> 00:06:33.369
Please take care of your devotee.
Always stay with me.

00:06:33.628 --> 00:06:35.561
Have a great time.

00:06:36.061 --> 00:06:38.680
Oh Mother, never leave me!

00:06:38.842 --> 00:06:40.611
Oh no. It has burnt too much.

00:06:42.638 --> 00:06:46.226
Master, you've been burning
the same incense stick for five years.

00:06:46.365 --> 00:06:47.892
Why don't you buy some new sticks?

00:06:48.026 --> 00:06:50.859
