just two loaves of bread a day?!

00:26:24.787 --> 00:26:26.287
You are just cheating!

00:26:26.436 --> 00:26:29.279
If you want to do business
with Hazari Prasad..

00:26:29.360 --> 00:26:31.610
..then you have to do it his way.

00:26:31.807 --> 00:26:35.831
What are you doing here?
Lakshmi is at your doorstep.

00:26:35.912 --> 00:26:37.037
Where is Lakshmi?

00:26:37.120 --> 00:26:40.120
This is Mr. Girdharilal,
whom I had told you about earlier.

00:26:40.203 --> 00:26:45.370
Mr. Girdharilal, please come in.
Have a seat.

00:26:45.953 --> 00:26:47.162
What can I do for you?

00:26:47.245 --> 00:26:51.037
He saw your son on the college stage.

00:26:51.120 --> 00:26:53.826
He likes your son.
- Wonderful!

00:26:53.937 --> 00:26:56.130
Murari, bring two cups of tea.
No. No.

00:26:56.221 --> 00:26:57.554
I got it, sir.

00:26:58.208 --> 00:27:02.190
I like your daughter.
- What are you expectations?

00:27:02.271 --> 00:27:03.816
Can you give me
an approximate number?

00:27:03.897 --> 00:27:07.855
Approximate number?
I have the complete list ready.

00:27:07.937 --> 00:27:09.812
Have a look. It is a small list.

00:27:24.808 --> 00:27:27.975
Mr. Hazari Prasad,
I am not a very rich person.

00:27:28.521 --> 00:27:31.229
Can you reduce some of your demands?

00:27:31.687 --> 00:27:34.437
If you want a discount,
go to some other shop for your daughter.

00:27:34.518 --> 00:27:38.852
Priest.
- I will, but let me tell you something.

00:27:39.354 --> 00:27:42.396
You buy and sell junk.
You are a junk-shop owner.

00:27:42.812 --> 00:27:44.437
Going by your demands..

00:27:44.521 --> 00:27:48.937
..you would have to marry off
your son to a millionaire's daughter.

00:27:50.481 --> 00:27:53.314
The whole world will
see and so will you.

00:27:53.437 --> 00:27:57.869
I will get my son married
to a millionaire's daughter.

00:27:58.729 --> 00:28:02.646
You've made me walk quite a lot.

00:28:02.727 --> 00:28:07.268
How much more do I have to walk?
- Just a little bit more.

00:28:07.349 --> 00:28:10.016
I'll die, if I walk even
one more step.

00:28:10.097 --> 00:28:12.931
Why do you want to kill me?

00:28:13.032 --> 00:28:14.699
Couldn't we take the bus?

00:28:14.780 --> 00:28:17.947
Why take a bus? We are almost there.

00:28:18.104 --> 00:28:20.316
We've already walked 10km,
just three more to go.

00:28:20.397 --> 00:28:22.986
Three km more? No, I won't walk.

00:28:23.067 --> 00:28:26.306
What are you doing? Get up. Go away.

00:28:26.437 --> 00:28:29.021
Why are you pushing us?
- The hotel's owner is coming.

00:28:35.354 --> 00:28:36.729
Good morning, sir.

00:28:37.937 --> 00:28:39.271
What were you saying, Varma?

00:28:39.354 --> 00:28:41.775
We've made profits of
50 lakhs from our Delhi hotel.

00:28:41.856 --> 00:28:45.647
50 lakhs! Don't waste my time.
50 lakhs is nothing.

00:28:45.771 --> 00:28:48.324
It's peanuts.
Do you know what a peanut is? - Peanuts.

00:28:51.746 --> 00:28:54.705
50 lakhs! Peanuts! Peanuts!

00:28:55.354 --> 00:28:58.937
We've made Rs.2 crore profit
from our London hotel, La Marina.

00:28:59.018 --> 00:29:01.313
Just two crores!
We were expecting four crores.

00:29:01.453 --> 00:29:03.703
This isn't profit. This is a loss.
- Sorry, sir.

00:29:08.350 --> 00:29:10.183
Today, you have an important meeting.
- With whom?

00:29:10.311 --> 00:29:12.836
About the proposal of
Mehra Group of hotels, Dubai.

00:29:12.940 --> 00:29:14.023
It's impossible today.

00:29:14.104 --> 00:29:16.475
Today is the 17th birthday
of my daughter, Madhu.

00:29:16.856 --> 00:29:19.564
We will lose lakhs of rupees.

00:29:19.812 --> 00:29:22.485
No. My daughter's birthday
comes once in a year.

00:29:22.729 --> 00:29:25.753
I can lose lakhs,
but I can't break her heart.

00:29:28.220 --> 00:29:30.262
A millionaire! With an only daughter!

00:29:30.343 --> 00:29:33.696
A millionaire! With an only daughter!
- Where are you?

00:29:33.813 --> 00:29:36.647
The bride's father is
waiting for you.

00:29:36.854 --> 00:29:37.699
Let's go.

00:29:39.521 --> 00:29:40.948
I've found the bride's father.

00:29:41.029 --> 00:29:45.779
What? - I'm the luckiest
person in this world!

00:29:46.104 --> 00:29:48.479
This millionaire?
- Yes!

00:29:49.173 --> 00:29:53.131
Even his cook's daughter
won't marry your son.

00:29:53.263 --> 00:29:55.388
He'll throw you out of his house.

00:29:55.469 --> 00:29:57.681
Or he will send you
to some mental asylum.

00:29:57.802 --> 00:29:59.927
Forget about this
alliance and come with me.

00:30:00.062 --> 00:30:01.619
The bride's father
will be waiting for you.

00:30:01.700 --> 00:30:05.367
Let me be.
You don't know about Hazari Prasad.

00:30:05.760 --> 00:30:08.802
I've found the millionaire
I was looking for.

00:30:09.115 --> 00:30:12.115
I will do anything..

00:30:12.437 --> 00:30:16.957
..to have my son marry
this millionaire's daughter.

00:30:32.556 --> 00:30:34.348
May God bless you.

00:30:39.326 --> 00:30:41.451
God bless you.

00:30:43.271 --> 00:30:45.854
Very good, Varma. Govind?
- I have taken the appointment.

00:30:45.937 --> 00:30:48.513
Shall we invite the quotations
of Bennet and Miranda?

00:30:48.594 --> 00:30:49.867
What's there to think about it?

00:30:50.051 --> 00:30:51.801
Tell them that..

00:30:57.696 --> 00:30:59.821
..Hazari Mills have made
lakhs of profit. - Next.

00:30:59.953 --> 00:31:02.120
There's an inauguration ceremony
of Hazari Chemicals today. - Next.

00:31:02.229 --> 00:31:04.822
There is also a meeting of
Hazari Shipping Corporation today.

00:31:05.795 --> 00:31:08.545
He looks like a very big personality.

00:31:09.114 --> 00:31:12.781
He must belong to a rich family,
like me.

00:31:16.979 --> 00:31:19.062
How much do I owe you?
- Rs.500.

00:31:19.146 --> 00:31:22.774
Rs.500! Are you crazy?
Rs.500 for four dogs?

00:31:22.854 --> 00:31:25.604
I could have hired 50 men instead.

00:31:25.687 --> 00:31:28.604
These days,
dogs are more important than men.

00:31:28.854 --> 00:31:29.684
Take this.

00:31:30.133 --> 00:31:33.062
Sir? -The dogs were small.
You cheat, take it.

00:31:33.146 --> 00:31:33.987
Sir..

00:31:34.604 --> 00:31:35.854
What role did you play?
- Secretary.

00:31:35.937 --> 00:31:37.816
What?
- Pay me quickly.

00:31:37.897 --> 00:31:40.063
I've got to go for the shooting.
Mr. Bachchan is waiting for me.

00:31:40.146 --> 00:31:42.687
How much do I owe you?
- Rs.400.

00:31:42.979 --> 00:31:45.354
It's stopped!
My heart has stopped beating.

00:31:45.593 --> 00:31:46.617
Rs.400.

00:31:52.271 --> 00:31:56.021
You'd rather have pet
dogs or be an actor, than rob.

00:31:57.189 --> 00:32:02.189
"No one's face is
as beautiful as you."

00:32:02.312 --> 00:32:05.229
Have you joined some theatre group?

00:32:05.311 --> 00:32:08.315
The dogs, the actors!
What's all this?

00:32:08.396 --> 00:32:10.562
This is business.
- Business!

00:32:10.643 --> 00:32:14.518
You won't understand. In this
business you make crores in profit..

00:32:14.615 --> 00:32:18.404
..by investing just lakhs of rupees.

00:32:19.521 --> 00:32:22.434
You are really great.
You are really gutsy.

00:32:22.515 --> 00:32:25.307
What have I done?
- Don't act so innocently.

00:32:25.600 --> 00:32:28.683
You have openly challenged
Karate Champion, Shakti..

00:32:28.764 --> 00:32:30.687
..and now you are asking
me what have I done?

00:32:30.771 --> 00:32:33.271
I have challenged Shakti?
- Yes, of course.

00:32:33.352 --> 00:32:34.772
That's what the whole
college is talking about.

00:32:34.853 --> 00:32:39.029
Raja will break Shakti's bones.
Raja's challenge.

00:32:39.110 --> 00:32:42.629
Shakti will walk in,
but he will go back on a stretcher.

00:32:42.769 --> 00:32:46.102
Raja's challenge.
- You are really gutsy.

00:32:46.271 --> 00:32:49.229
Raja will die in style.

00:32:49.310 --> 00:32:52.685
What rubbish. I've got
nothing to do with these posters.

00:32:52.771 --> 00:32:54.062
What?
- Yes.

00:32:54.146 --> 00:32:56.067
Then whose mischief is this?

00:32:58.854 --> 00:33:02.021
Cowards run away
when they are losing.

00:33:02.251 --> 00:33:05.251
But some cowards are too arrogant.

00:33:06.315 --> 00:33:08.190
He will die a young death.

00:33:08.271 --> 00:33:11.835
I shouldn't be saying this,
but Raja is finished!

00:33:14.407 --> 00:33:18.896
I won't let it happen.
I will remove these posters right now.

00:33:19.021 --> 00:33:22.854
Buddy, if you remove the
posters I will be disgraced.

00:33:23.521 --> 00:33:24.739
Let's see what happens.

00:33:24.820 --> 00:33:26.987
I hope it's not your funeral.

00:33:27.104 --> 00:33:30.045
Shakti. Shakti. Shakti. Shakti.

00:33:30.126 --> 00:33:33.365
Shakti. Shakti. Shakti. Shakti.

00:33:33.446 --> 00:33:36.655
Raja hasn't shown up.
I guess he won't come.

00:33:36.946 --> 00:33:38.222
Maybe he has given up.

00:33:38.303 --> 00:33:41.553
Raja! Raja! Raja! Raja!

00:33:41.946 --> 00:33:44.876
Raja! Raja! Raja! Raja!

00:33:45.027 --> 00:33:47.277
Raja! Raja! Ra..

00:33:50.220 --> 00:33:53.470
Raja! Raja! Raja!

00:34:07.913 --> 00:34:11.256
Shakti. Shakti. Shakti. Shakti.

00:34:11.571 --> 00:34:17.486
Friends, we have with us three-time
college champion, Mr. Shakti.

00:34:18.646 --> 00:34:20.077
Give him a big hand.

00:34:23.237 --> 00:34:24.894
Quiet!

00:34:26.280 --> 00:34:30.155
He is Mr. Raja.

00:34:33.571 --> 00:34:38.946
He has shown great courage
by challenging Shakti, but..

00:34:39.155 --> 00:34:44.988
..we'd be doing injustice to
Raja if we don't give him a last chance.

00:34:45.489 --> 00:34:47.323
To save himself from
being humiliated..

00:34:47.577 --> 00:34:50.182
..Raja can still refuse to fight.

00:34:50.280 --> 00:34:52.863
This is your chance to refuse.

00:34:53.024 --> 00:34:54.608
But there is a condition.

00:34:55.114 --> 00:34:59.240
He would apologise to Shakti..

00:34:59.446 --> 00:35:02.780
..by touching his feet
in front of everyone.

00:35:09.655 --> 00:35:14.280
I am ready to fight,
but I too have a condition.

00:35:14.648 --> 00:35:18.696
If Miss. Madhu has the guts
then she should accept my condition.

00:35:19.771 --> 00:35:21.071
What's the condition?

00:35:22.128 --> 00:35:26.280
The condition is that if I win..

00:35:27.109 --> 00:35:33.488
..I will kiss Madhu
in front of everyone.

00:35:38.571 --> 00:35:42.196
Okay. I accept it..

00:35:42.710 --> 00:35:44.293
..but I too have a condition.

00:35:44.789 --> 00:35:50.338
If Mr. Raja loses,
he will kiss my friend, Miss Mimi.

00:35:50.863 --> 00:35:52.696
Miss. Mimi.

00:36:05.957 --> 00:36:07.123
I accept it.

00:36:09.030 --> 00:36:13.780
But if Mr. Shakti loses,
he will kiss Miss Mimi.

00:36:19.797 --> 00:36:22.588
Ready. Fight.

00:36:41.755 --> 00:36:43.130
Come on.

00:36:51.815 --> 00:36:53.190
Come on, Shakti.

00:37:00.040 --> 00:37:01.116
Beat him!

00:37:15.198 --> 00:37:16.083
Hey!

00:37:18.532 --> 00:37:21.122
Shakti. Shakti. Shakti. Shakti.

00:37:21.318 --> 00:37:22.657
Here Raja.

00:37:22.854 --> 00:37:26.988
Shakti. Shakti. Shakti. Shakti.

00:37:48.847 --> 00:37:49.921
Beat him, Raja!

00:37:50.920 --> 00:37:51.815
Get him!

00:37:57.766 --> 00:38:01.391
1-2-3-4.

00:38:01.472 --> 00:38:04.889
5-6-7.

00:38:34.808 --> 00:38:36.171
Shakti, get up.

00:38:41.808 --> 00:38:42.870
Come on, Shakti.

00:38:56.183 --> 00:38:58.558
1-2.
- Shakti, get up.

00:38:58.915 --> 00:39:03.560
3-4-5-6..

00:39:03.700 --> 00:39:04.891
Come on, Shakti, get up.

00:39:05.022 --> 00:39:08.147
8-9 and 10.
- Get up!

00:39:08.350 --> 00:39:09.933
Oh, no.

00:39:10.600 --> 00:39:15.808
Raja! Raja! Raja! Raja!

00:39:15.937 --> 00:39:17.170
Silence.

00:39:19.058 --> 00:39:22.391
Friends, as per the conditions..

00:39:22.808 --> 00:39:28.058
..our new Champion
Raja will kiss Miss Madhu..

00:39:28.316 --> 00:39:32.016
..in front of everyone.

00:39:42.100 --> 00:39:44.770
Miss. Madhu, please come. Welcome.

00:39:44.850 --> 00:39:46.818
Friends, give her a big hand.

00:40:49.141 --> 00:40:51.475
When I was younger I was taught..

00:40:52.096 --> 00:40:55.013
..to always stay away
from unimportant people.

00:40:59.225 --> 00:41:03.641
Raja! Raja! Raja! Raja!

00:41:03.766 --> 00:41:11.817
Raja! Raja! Raja! Raja!

00:41:18.808 --> 00:41:20.850
No.

00:41:28.933 --> 00:41:32.183
Son, are you going to the temple?
- Yes, Mother.

00:41:32.923 --> 00:41:35.308
Have you thought about Madhu?

00:41:35.391 --> 00:41:37.475
That's why I am going to the temple.

00:41:37.725 --> 00:41:40.141
I am going to request
God to do something about her..

00:41:40.225 --> 00:41:41.266
..and I'll also try to do my bit.

00:41:41.350 --> 00:41:43.058
But where is Madhu?

00:41:44.516 --> 00:41:47.683
There you are.
- Daddy, I want a goli (bullet).

00:41:47.766 --> 00:41:50.933
Didn't Ramu give you
the vitamin goli?

00:41:51.016 --> 00:41:54.516
I need a bullet.
- Bullet!

00:41:54.600 --> 00:41:55.728
What happened?

00:41:55.808 --> 00:41:57.808
I will kill that scum.

00:41:58.141 --> 00:42:01.725
Until I shoot him,
I won't have my breakfast.

00:42:01.959 --> 00:42:02.959
What happened?

00:42:03.350 --> 00:42:06.516
He insulted me in front of everyone.

00:42:06.641 --> 00:42:08.225
Insulted you?! How?

00:42:08.433 --> 00:42:09.891
He held me in front of everyone..

00:42:10.016 --> 00:42:11.808
What did he do to you?

00:42:13.058 --> 00:42:14.183
He did nothing.

00:42:14.391 --> 00:42:17.701
He did nothing?
Then how were you insulted?

00:42:18.016 --> 00:42:20.350
Let her speak.
- Good morning, Uncle.

00:42:20.579 --> 00:42:22.560
Hello.
- Greetings, grandma.

00:42:22.641 --> 00:42:23.808
Greetings!
- Hi!

00:42:23.891 --> 00:42:25.475
What happened to you?

00:42:26.058 --> 00:42:28.350
Are you alright?
- I am absolutely fine.

00:42:28.475 --> 00:42:30.794
But your lips look swollen.
- What?

00:42:31.145 --> 00:42:34.350
No, sir. The thing is..

00:42:35.641 --> 00:42:38.350
..I'm boxing a bit too much.

00:42:38.475 --> 00:42:41.141
Don't box so much..

00:42:41.350 --> 00:42:42.933
..or else it will
be hard to recognise you.

00:42:43.141 --> 00:42:44.475
When is your father
coming back from London?

00:42:44.641 --> 00:42:46.165
Next week.
- Next week! - Yes.

00:42:46.246 --> 00:42:47.894
I forgot. I had to go to the temple.

00:42:47.975 --> 00:42:50.058
You keep talking. I am leaving.
- Ok.

00:42:58.691 --> 00:42:59.732
Take it.

00:43:00.386 --> 00:43:02.753
Hail to you.
- Hail to you.

00:43:03.346 --> 00:43:04.593
God bless you.
- Be happy.

00:43:04.674 --> 00:43:08.350
Our saviour is here.
Our Almighty is here. - He is here.

00:43:08.516 --> 00:43:09.850
Our God is here.

00:43:09.975 --> 00:43:14.728
Our God is here.
Long live our master.

00:43:14.808 --> 00:43:16.600
Get up.

00:43:17.516 --> 00:43:19.975
Greetings.
- Who is he?

00:43:20.100 --> 00:43:21.808
He looks like a reincarnation of God.

00:43:21.891 --> 00:43:24.433
Please sit, everyone will get it.
- Sit down. Don't rush.

00:43:24.891 --> 00:43:26.891
Take this.
- Sit quietly.

00:43:27.016 --> 00:43:29.016
He'll give you, sit quietly.
- You take it as well.

00:43:29.865 --> 00:43:30.683
Take this.

00:43:33.058 --> 00:43:35.891
What would've happened to
us if you had not been there for us?

00:43:36.058 --> 00:43:39.683
I think that I am poorer than you.

00:43:39.891 --> 00:43:41.435
God has given me so much money..

00:43:41.516 --> 00:43:43.641
..but he has given
me just two hands to give.

00:43:43.725 --> 00:43:47.376
I wish he'd have given
me 1,000 hands to donate.

00:43:49.266 --> 00:43:51.183
God bless you!

00:43:58.899 --> 00:44:04.149
Mother Goddess,
you have given me so much wealth.

00:44:04.725 --> 00:44:08.183
But still,
I come to you everyday as a beggar.

00:44:08.600 --> 00:44:10.058
I beg to you.

00:44:10.433 --> 00:44:12.350
The way you have given
me so much wealth..

00:44:12.863 --> 00:44:14.947
..give me a good daughter-in-law.

00:44:15.225 --> 00:44:17.558
I don't want anything else.

00:44:17.988 --> 00:44:21.238
I just want a good daughter-in-law.

00:44:21.475 --> 00:44:24.641
Mother. Give me
a good daughter-in-law.

00:44:24.933 --> 00:44:28.850
Give me a good daughter-in-law.

00:44:36.933 --> 00:44:38.118
Yes, sir.

00:44:38.811 --> 00:44:40.227
Go.
- Yes, sir.

00:44:41.433 --> 00:44:42.343
Mother.

00:44:53.808 --> 00:44:56.641
The tyres have been punctured.
- Don't you have any spare tyres?

00:44:56.874 --> 00:44:58.963
We have only one spare tyre,
but two tyres are punctured.

00:44:59.058 --> 00:45:02.100
I had such an important meeting
and there is no phone around..

00:45:02.183 --> 00:45:04.322
If you don't mind,
I can give you a lift.

00:45:04.403 --> 00:45:07.278
I will drop you wherever you want.
- Don't trouble yourself.

00:45:07.683 --> 00:45:10.433
Take this. Give us a sandwich.

00:45:10.753 --> 00:45:12.795
A Rs.100 note.
How did you get a Rs.100 note?

00:45:12.891 --> 00:45:15.410
Why do you care?
- Okay.

00:45:17.225 --> 00:45:19.891
This is a fake currency note.

00:45:20.071 --> 00:45:24.058
Take it away.
I'll take you to the police. Go away.

00:45:24.141 --> 00:45:26.766
A fake note? Ramu.
- Mine is also a fake note.

00:45:26.850 --> 00:45:29.475
Your? - Mine, too.
- Where is that man?

00:45:29.683 --> 00:45:32.350
There's no problem at all.
Please come. - There he is.

00:45:32.431 --> 00:45:34.098
It's very sweet of you.
Thank you very much. God bless you.

00:45:34.225 --> 00:45:35.391
Catch him!

00:45:37.641 --> 00:45:39.975
You gave us fake notes.
You fooled us.

00:45:40.100 --> 00:45:41.308
Goodbye.

00:45:43.016 --> 00:45:45.475
They love you a lot.

00:45:46.100 --> 00:45:48.350
They respect you more than God.

00:45:48.641 --> 00:45:50.225
It's just their affection.

00:45:50.683 --> 00:45:53.725
No one can become a God
by donating some 10 to 20 lakhs.

00:45:53.847 --> 00:45:55.308
Drive faster.

00:45:55.391 --> 00:45:58.850
