and return these bangles. Go!

02:05:30.736 --> 02:05:33.320
I have not behaved
properly with Raja.

02:05:34.486 --> 02:05:36.403
Without any reason, I made him upset.

02:05:37.486 --> 02:05:40.320
Poor guy.
He left without even eating anything.

02:05:41.903 --> 02:05:45.403
When he comes back,
I'll ask him to forgive me.

02:05:45.969 --> 02:05:47.802
I will feed him with my own hands.

02:05:51.188 --> 02:05:52.521
It is evening now.

02:05:53.331 --> 02:05:55.331
Why hasn't Raja come back yet?

02:05:56.028 --> 02:05:57.445
Did anything happen..

02:05:57.738 --> 02:06:00.280
No. This cannot happen.

02:06:00.986 --> 02:06:02.653
He has gotten angry
with me and went away.

02:06:02.820 --> 02:06:03.986
Wherever he is right now..

02:06:04.070 --> 02:06:05.986
..I will convince
him and bring him back.

02:06:08.820 --> 02:06:11.986
Ramu hit his son a lot.
I was unable to tolerate it.

02:06:12.153 --> 02:06:15.246
I explained it to him well.
But he did not understand.

02:06:15.486 --> 02:06:17.111
He went on hitting him.
- Uncle!

02:06:17.403 --> 02:06:20.361
Did Raja come here?
- No, daughter. He did not come here.

02:06:21.736 --> 02:06:23.153
Then where did he go?

02:06:23.736 --> 02:06:24.986
What happened, dear?

02:08:09.153 --> 02:08:10.653
Where were you for such a long time?

02:08:11.861 --> 02:08:12.780
Answer me!

02:08:16.153 --> 02:08:18.111
