02:09:21.361 --> 02:09:25.070
..a married woman's wrist
should never be void of any bangles?

02:09:30.420 --> 02:09:34.379
I am sorry. Please forgive me.

02:09:37.111 --> 02:09:38.249
I am sorry.

02:09:40.794 --> 02:09:44.505
