will never leave me.

02:09:47.070 --> 02:09:49.111
I don't want anything
else besides you.

02:09:49.736 --> 02:09:51.111
Nothing else!

02:09:52.111 --> 02:09:53.820
I love you, Raja!

02:10:00.195 --> 02:10:01.152
