02:12:44.445 --> 02:12:48.986
The lover upstairs
will kiss his dear wife.

02:12:49.130 --> 02:12:50.839
All right.

02:12:51.447 --> 02:12:52.864
Hey, daughter!

02:12:52.945 --> 02:12:58.294
What do you say..
He is coming downstairs to kiss you.

02:13:00.988 --> 02:13:02.405
Aunt.
- Yes.

02:13:02.505 --> 02:13:05.630
Tell him not to come down.
I am going home.

02:13:05.788 --> 02:13:08.614
Madhu! Please don't go. I am coming.

02:13:08.695 --> 02:13:11.570
Don't come down! I am leaving.

02:13:11.695 --> 02:13:12.943
I am coming.

02:13:20.884 --> 02:13:22.285
Raja!

02:13:39.455 --> 02:13:42.330
Yes, Doctor. It's an emergency.
Please come immediately.

02:13:42.695 --> 02:13:44.156
Nurse, arrange for the blood.
- Yes, sir.

02:13:44.240 --> 02:13:45.596
Doctor, do the arrangements
for the operation. - Yes, sir.

02:13:45.677 --> 02:13:46.530
Please. Hurry up!

02:13:46.611 --> 02:13:49.986
Please save my Raja!
- We are trying our level best, Madam.

02:13:50.375 --> 02:13:51.708
The patient's condition
is very serious.

02:13:51.861 --> 02:13:54.028
You arrange for at least Rs.1 lakh.

02:13:54.528 --> 02:13:56.070
You don't worry about the money,
Doctor.

02:13:56.184 --> 02:13:58.809
I will bring as much money as possible.
You just arrange for the operation.

02:14:20.070 --> 02:14:22.653
Madam, where are you going?
Sir and grandma have gone out.

02:14:23.028 --> 02:14:24.028
Where have they gone?

02:14:24.109 --> 02:14:26.067
They have gone out of town.
I don't know when they'll return.

02:14:46.972 --> 02:14:50.014
You! For what have you come here?
Go away!

02:14:50.095 --> 02:14:52.563
Listen to me at least.
Raja has met with an accident.

02:14:52.644 --> 02:14:54.560
What? Where is Raja?

02:14:54.695 --> 02:14:56.611
He is breathing his
last in the hospital now.

02:14:57.195 --> 02:15:00.236
We have to get him operated.
I need Rs.1 lakh for that.

02:15:00.403 --> 02:15:02.278
If the operation is not
done as soon as possible..

02:15:02.361 --> 02:15:03.697
..then he may not survive.

02:15:03.963 --> 02:15:06.236
Please save my Raja!
Please save my Raja!

02:15:06.361 --> 02:15:07.861
Please take me to my Raja.

02:15:08.028 --> 02:15:09.155
Fine. You both go to the hospital.

02:15:09.236 --> 02:15:11.313
I will bring the money and come there.
- Let's go!

02:15:25.733 --> 02:15:27.566
Have you gone mad, Hazari Prasad?

02:15:28.047 --> 02:15:29.547
You are being sentimental
about your son..

02:15:29.653 --> 02:15:31.820
..and helping your enemy's daughter.

02:15:32.155 --> 02:15:33.739
Have you forgotten the
day when that scum, Mehra..

02:15:33.820 --> 02:15:35.736
..had slapped you
amongst a huge gathering?

02:15:36.153 --> 02:15:39.570
Hazari Prasad, this is the
right moment to avenge your insult.

02:15:39.695 --> 02:15:41.028
Do not let it slip
off from your hands.

02:15:41.153 --> 02:15:43.028
Do not let it slip off from your hands,
Hazari Prasad.

02:15:49.620 --> 02:15:51.995
Mother, why hasn't father come yet?

02:15:52.630 --> 02:15:53.964
Don't worry, dear.

02:15:54.236 --> 02:15:55.861
He must be on his way with the money.

02:16:01.861 --> 02:16:02.719
Wait!

02:16:06.153 --> 02:16:07.778
You love Raja very much, isn't it?

02:16:10.861 --> 02:16:13.486
Then what can you do for Raja?
- Anything.

02:16:13.861 --> 02:16:15.861
But let Raja get operated first.

02:16:15.986 --> 02:16:18.070
Every second is
very precious for him.

02:16:19.361 --> 02:16:20.778
And Raja is precious for me.

02:16:21.028 --> 02:16:22.153
Then what do you want?

02:16:22.528 --> 02:16:24.230
Your Mangalsutra
(Symbol of marriage).

02:16:28.114 --> 02:16:31.030
What are you saying?
Have you gone mad?

02:16:31.111 --> 02:16:32.903
Mad people do not
speak in their senses.

02:16:33.028 --> 02:16:35.102
Do not instigate a
married woman to curse you.

02:16:35.403 --> 02:16:38.403
A married woman's
curse changes destiny.

02:16:38.736 --> 02:16:42.028
Then whatever happens,
even God cannot change it.

02:16:42.111 --> 02:16:44.945
I don't know what form
her curse would take.

02:16:45.028 --> 02:16:47.070
Stop this rubbish!
Or you'll have to face the consequences.

02:16:47.153 --> 02:16:50.028
You are not a human being.
You are a demon. You are a beast!

02:16:50.109 --> 02:16:51.447
Yes. I am a demon. I am a beast.

02:16:51.599 --> 02:16:54.320
But who turned me into a beast?
This girl's father.

02:16:54.469 --> 02:16:56.360
He has embarrassed me.
He has insulted me.

02:16:56.445 --> 02:16:58.153
He slapped me amongst
a huge gathering.

02:16:58.236 --> 02:17:00.278
But why are you making the
daughter pay for her father's mistake?

02:17:00.403 --> 02:17:01.820
Give the bag to me!

02:17:04.111 --> 02:17:06.236
Do not dare to
interfere in my affairs.

02:17:06.361 --> 02:17:08.486
Get lost from here. Otherwise
our relationship will come to an end.

02:17:08.566 --> 02:17:10.149
Go away from here. Go!
- Listen to me.

02:17:10.236 --> 02:17:11.703
Go away from here!

02:17:13.195 --> 02:17:14.695
Now you listen to me carefully.

02:17:14.778 --> 02:17:16.861
If your husband dies then
don't hold me responsible.

02:17:17.353 --> 02:17:20.437
I plead to you.
For God's sake, please don't do this.

02:17:20.519 --> 02:17:22.166
I am not doing all this for God.
I am doing all this for my sake.

02:17:22.278 --> 02:17:25.778
But if Raja is my husband
he is your son, too.

02:17:25.859 --> 02:17:28.484
My son died the day
he got married to you..

02:17:28.695 --> 02:17:30.570
..and put this Mangalsutra
around your neck.

02:17:30.695 --> 02:17:33.077
My success lies in this necklace.
Give it to me.

02:17:34.607 --> 02:17:36.357
This is not just
an ordinary necklace.

02:17:37.320 --> 02:17:39.570
In each black bead of this
necklace all those nights..

02:17:39.651 --> 02:17:41.361
..of Karva Chauth (Fasting day
for husband's long life) are entwined..

02:17:41.653 --> 02:17:44.528
..when I had prayed for
the well being of my husband.

02:17:44.898 --> 02:17:47.148
If you would have asked me for my life
I would have gladly given it to you.

02:17:47.589 --> 02:17:49.630
But how can I give
my Mangalsutra to you?

02:17:50.153 --> 02:17:52.986
You are wasting your tears and my time,
you foolish girl!

02:17:53.070 --> 02:17:55.236
I am leaving.
- No!

02:17:55.361 --> 02:17:59.195
Please don't do this.
Please do not separate me from Raja.

02:17:59.320 --> 02:18:01.153
I cannot live without him.

02:18:01.268 --> 02:18:03.310
I will die.

02:18:03.403 --> 02:18:04.496
Then die!

02:18:05.070 --> 02:18:06.000
Stop!

02:18:07.070 --> 02:18:10.694
I am ready to do whatever you say.

02:18:15.778 --> 02:18:18.361
Come on. Swear by your husband that..

02:18:18.445 --> 02:18:21.070
..after today, there won't be any
relation between him and you. Come on.

02:18:21.903 --> 02:18:23.280
From today onwards,
you will not meet him.

02:18:23.361 --> 02:18:24.724
You will never ever cross his path.

02:18:24.805 --> 02:18:26.840
You'll never tell him
why you stopped meeting him.

02:18:26.921 --> 02:18:28.921
I bind with the oath of the
relationship of a husband and wife.

02:18:29.002 --> 02:18:30.649
From now on you and Raja
are not husband and wife.

02:18:30.745 --> 02:18:34.245
If you break this promise,
you'll see Raja dead. - No.

02:18:34.903 --> 02:18:38.195
I agree. I agree.

02:19:16.111 --> 02:19:23.403
"You should always be alive."

02:19:23.695 --> 02:19:29.736
"I pray only for that."

02:19:30.403 --> 02:19:37.820
"If death comes, let it take me."

02:19:38.181 --> 02:19:43.931
"You should be spared all the pain."

02:19:44.861 --> 02:19:51.945
"I have just done it once.
I have fallen in love with you."

02:19:52.028 --> 02:19:59.945
"I have just done it once.
I have fallen in love with you."

02:20:04.278 --> 02:20:05.138
Dear..

02:20:05.800 --> 02:20:07.703
Doctor. How is my Raja?
Please tell me, Doctor.

02:20:07.784 --> 02:20:09.090
There is no need to worry now.

02:20:09.210 --> 02:20:11.710
He is out of danger.
If you want, you can see him.

02:21:11.330 --> 02:21:13.986
Hey, what happened?
- Hey! He has dashed a girl!

02:21:15.086 --> 02:21:16.121
Oh God!

02:21:17.226 --> 02:21:19.267
Excuse me. Move.

02:21:20.486 --> 02:21:24.572
Oh my God! Madhu! Daughter!

02:21:25.922 --> 02:21:28.361
Guard. Driver, bring some water.
- Sir, water.

02:21:33.250 --> 02:21:34.292
My child!

02:21:36.653 --> 02:21:37.778
Daddy!

02:21:38.486 --> 02:21:40.653
Daddy, I want to die.
- No.

02:21:40.903 --> 02:21:44.486
I want to die. - No, child.
I'll not let you die, my daughter.

02:21:44.820 --> 02:21:47.278
Who has done this to you? Who is he?

02:22:01.070 --> 02:22:03.445
Mr. Mehra!
What is this that I am seeing?

02:22:03.695 --> 02:22:06.611
A rich man's daughter,
in this condition.

02:22:07.044 --> 02:22:09.185
It seems she has
not eaten for many days.

02:22:09.266 --> 02:22:11.570
Whereas Mr. Mehra has four hotels.

02:22:12.155 --> 02:22:13.155
Look at her clothes!

02:22:13.236 --> 02:22:15.153
She doesn't even have proper
clothes to cover herself.

02:22:15.234 --> 02:22:17.859
Mr. Mehra has six mills of cloth.

02:22:18.153 --> 02:22:20.153
Ladies and gentlemen,
maybe you all don't know him..

02:22:20.236 --> 02:22:22.403
..but I know Mr. Mehra very well.

02:22:22.778 --> 02:22:26.153
Seeing all this,
I am unable to believe my eyes.

02:22:26.570 --> 02:22:28.361
The daughter whose
one sob would shake..

02:22:28.486 --> 02:22:30.653
..the very foundation
of Mehra Industries..

02:22:31.153 --> 02:22:32.820
..the same daughter
is like a corpse today.

02:22:32.903 --> 02:22:33.830
Hazari!

02:22:34.111 --> 02:22:36.570
There is no use of shouting,
Mr. Mehra.

02:22:36.737 --> 02:22:39.029
Just have some pity on
your daughter's condition!

02:22:39.361 --> 02:22:45.223
So gentlemen, this helpless girl
fell in love and ran away from home.

02:22:45.986 --> 02:22:50.041
As it always happens,
her lover threw her out of the house.

02:22:50.653 --> 02:22:52.778
Now why did he throw her out?
I don't know anything about that.

02:22:52.861 --> 02:22:54.445
Only Mr. Mehra
can enlighten you on that.

02:22:54.653 --> 02:22:57.236
But I have a request.

02:22:57.871 --> 02:23:00.121
If there is some good marriage
proposal then let him know.

02:23:00.403 --> 02:23:01.653
Do not worry about the money.

02:23:01.820 --> 02:23:04.861
Mr. Mehra has lots of money!
You will get a big dowry.

02:23:04.945 --> 02:23:07.403
We are not so shameless that
we will use the things which others..

02:23:07.486 --> 02:23:08.882
..have used and thrown.

02:23:10.195 --> 02:23:11.653
Did you hear him, Mr. Mehra?

02:23:11.945 --> 02:23:14.153
Now your daughter has
just two options left.

02:23:14.508 --> 02:23:17.341
Either she commits suicide
or she can become a prostitute.

02:23:17.445 --> 02:23:20.438
Shut your mouth, Hazari!
- You shut your mouth, Mehra!

02:23:23.695 --> 02:23:27.695
Take my shawl and cover this corpse.

02:23:27.903 --> 02:23:31.611
It is a bit worn out because
it belongs to a scrap vendor.

02:23:31.945 --> 02:23:34.945
But it is sufficient to
cover your daughter's dignity.

02:23:35.528 --> 02:23:40.361
Also take this bowl and start
begging for your daughter's life.

02:23:41.195 --> 02:23:43.528
Remember one thing, Mehra.

02:23:44.653 --> 02:23:49.403
The slap that cannot
be seen hurts more.

02:23:52.070 --> 02:23:53.611
Idiot!

02:23:59.028 --> 02:24:01.063
You beast.

02:24:03.736 --> 02:24:06.153
Take this, child. Have the medicine.

02:24:07.237 --> 02:24:09.526
First tell me, where is Madhu?

02:24:11.320 --> 02:24:13.028
Whenever I ask you,
you always evade the issue.

02:24:14.611 --> 02:24:16.320
Why don't you tell me where is she?

02:24:16.736 --> 02:24:18.611
How is she? She is fine, isn't it?

02:24:18.986 --> 02:24:20.945
However she is, I want to see her.
I want to meet her.

02:24:21.153 --> 02:24:23.736
Where is Madhu, Mother?
- Do you want to know where Madhu is?

02:24:24.283 --> 02:24:25.325
How she is?

02:24:25.570 --> 02:24:26.820
Then listen to me, son.

02:24:27.236 --> 02:24:30.486
The Madhu,
for whom you are in so much pain..

02:24:30.695 --> 02:24:32.945
..has left you and gone
back to her father's house.

02:24:33.153 --> 02:24:35.945
No! You are telling lies!
This is not possible.

02:24:36.028 --> 02:24:39.653
Then why didn't she come to meet
you when you were fighting with death?

02:24:39.751 --> 02:24:41.334
Because she was enjoying
herself at her father's house.

02:24:41.528 --> 02:24:42.986
Thank God we reached there in time.

02:24:43.070 --> 02:24:44.570
Otherwise there was
nobody to take care of you.

02:24:44.653 --> 02:24:47.111
No! My Madhu cannot do this.

02:24:47.260 --> 02:24:48.569
She cannot betray me.

02:24:48.861 --> 02:24:51.653
Daddy, she can die for me,
but she cannot leave me alone to die.

02:24:51.736 --> 02:24:53.945
You foolish boy!
The girl whom you are considering..

02:24:54.028 --> 02:24:55.820
..to be your wife,
your beloved, your lover.

02:24:55.903 --> 02:24:57.445
The girl whom you had married.

02:24:57.556 --> 02:24:59.139
The girl around whose neck
you had put the holy Mangalsutra..

02:24:59.238 --> 02:25:00.280
..she threw it on my face.

02:25:00.361 --> 02:25:02.403
The Mangalsutra which
you had given to her. Look.

02:25:06.662 --> 02:25:08.412
You are telling lies.
You are telling lies.

02:25:08.570 --> 02:25:11.736
If you trust your eyes more than
my word then go and see it for yourself.

02:25:11.827 --> 02:25:14.435
See whether your Madhu
even recognises you. Go and see.

02:25:15.620 --> 02:25:17.345
Madhu!

02:25:25.111 --> 02:25:26.369
Madhu!

02:25:42.405 --> 02:25:44.405
Swear by the pure relationship
of a husband and wife.

02:25:44.486 --> 02:25:46.236
From today onwards,
Raja and you are not husband and wife.

02:25:46.317 --> 02:25:49.484
And if you break this promise
then you will see Raja dead.

02:25:50.861 --> 02:25:51.720
Hi, Madhu!

02:25:53.778 --> 02:25:55.111
I have brought flowers for you.

02:26:01.611 --> 02:26:04.653
Come, Shakti!
- You are looking gorgeous.

02:26:06.028 --> 02:26:08.851
You are so nice.
You care so much for me.

02:26:24.280 --> 02:26:25.863
Come, Shakti.
- Yes, come on.

02:26:28.320 --> 02:26:30.611
Raja, you!

02:26:31.195 --> 02:26:32.211
Why?

02:26:33.381 --> 02:26:35.339
Are you upset to see me alive?

02:26:39.611 --> 02:26:44.153
Madhu, I never thought
that you would stoop so low.

02:26:46.361 --> 02:26:47.861
When my father told me that..

02:26:48.611 --> 02:26:52.028
..you left me alone in the
hospital in critical condition..

02:26:53.028 --> 02:26:55.111
..I did not believe him.

02:26:56.643 --> 02:27:00.768
But now I have realised
that my father was right..

02:27:01.945 --> 02:27:03.916
..and my love was false.

02:27:08.028 --> 02:27:09.278
Why are you quiet, Madhu?

02:27:10.404 --> 02:27:11.319
Answer me.

02:27:13.364 --> 02:27:14.572
Say something, Madhu.

02:27:14.653 --> 02:27:16.361
What was lacking in my love?

02:27:17.445 --> 02:27:19.236
Madhu, what wrong had I done that..

02:27:19.445 --> 02:27:21.320
..you punished me so badly?

02:27:22.486 --> 02:27:25.903
Look Raja, I have been used
to a luxurious life since my childhood.

02:27:26.653 --> 02:27:29.437
By staying with you,
my requirements couldn't be fulfilled.

02:27:32.138 --> 02:27:35.680
Moreover, after your accident,
neither did I want to live as a widow..

02:27:36.111 --> 02:27:38.528
..nor did I want to
live as a cripple's wife.

02:27:41.945 --> 02:27:44.275
No. No, Shakti.

02:27:46.820 --> 02:27:48.111
Let him go.

02:27:48.903 --> 02:27:50.611
This poor fellow is
not in his senses right now.

02:27:50.695 --> 02:27:52.486
In fact,
I have come to my senses now.

02:27:53.903 --> 02:27:57.820
I have loved you, Madhu.
I will always love you.

02:27:58.736 --> 02:28:02.695
But whatever you did to me,
please don't tell it to anybody.

02:28:03.611 --> 02:28:05.861
Otherwise people
will lose faith in love.

02:28:59.153 --> 02:29:02.957
Raja! I love you!

02:29:03.953 --> 02:29:07.072
I love you!

02:29:07.153 --> 02:29:10.403
I love you!

02:29:10.486 --> 02:29:13.403
I love you!

02:29:13.615 --> 02:29:17.143
I love you!

02:29:38.778 --> 02:29:43.986
"Oh my beloved!"

02:29:45.751 --> 02:29:52.084
"Why did you forget me?"

02:29:53.403 --> 02:29:59.945
"Disloyal or cruel."

02:30:00.461 --> 02:30:04.878
"What do I call you, my darling?"

02:30:05.570 --> 02:30:08.776
"You have broken my heart."

02:30:08.857 --> 02:30:11.780
"What wrong have I done?
Please let me know."

02:30:11.861 --> 02:30:18.236
"Oh my beloved!
I am your darling lover."

02:30:18.403 --> 02:30:21.528
"I have tolerated all my tears."

02:30:21.653 --> 02:30:24.528
"I have survived through
lots of difficulties."

02:30:24.820 --> 02:30:30.628
"What is my helplessness?
How do I tell you about that?"

02:30:30.709 --> 02:30:33.667
"Oh my beloved!"

02:30:33.785 --> 02:30:38.035
"Why did you forget me?"

02:31:19.195 --> 02:31:25.570
"If I had known that
you are a disloyal woman."

02:31:25.695 --> 02:31:32.820
"Then I would never have
fallen in love with you."

02:31:35.016 --> 02:31:41.239
"If I had known that
you are a disloyal woman."

02:31:41.391 --> 02:31:47.391
"Then I would never have
fallen in love with you."

02:31:47.573 --> 02:31:53.698
"Trust me.
Do not blame me like this."

02:31:53.861 --> 02:31:59.903
"Punish me if you want. But
please do not call me a disloyal woman."

02:32:00.111 --> 02:32:06.153
"My beloved! You have betrayed me."

02:32:06.310 --> 02:32:12.018
"But my loyalty will
never be able to forget you."

02:32:12.111 --> 02:32:18.736
"Oh my beloved!
I am your darling lover."

02:32:18.817 --> 02:32:21.708
"I have tolerated all my tears."

02:32:21.834 --> 02:32:24.876
"I have survived through
lots of difficulties."

02:32:25.028 --> 02:32:30.695
"What is my helplessness?
How do I tell you about that?"

02:32:30.813 --> 02:32:33.813
"Oh my beloved!"

02:32:33.945 --> 02:32:39.278
"Why did you forget me?"

02:33:31.544 --> 02:33:37.929
"I feel like ruining myself."

02:33:38.010 --> 02:33:45.176
"I feel like embracing death."

02:33:47.153 --> 02:33:53.153
"I feel like ruining myself."

02:33:53.460 --> 02:33:59.364
"I feel like embracing death."

02:33:59.445 --> 02:34:05.570
"Come and look into my
heart by tearing it apart."

02:34:05.739 --> 02:34:11.822
"You will find the colours
of your pictures in it."

02:34:11.903 --> 02:34:17.903
"Oh my darling.
You may live peacefully."

02:34:18.028 --> 02:34:23.611
"This is the wish
of my broken heart."

02:34:23.820 --> 02:34:30.320
"Oh my beloved!
I am your darling lover."

02:34:30.445 --> 02:34:33.611
"I have tolerated all my tears."

02:34:33.692 --> 02:34:36.192
"I have survived through
lots of difficulties."

02:34:36.611 --> 02:34:42.392
"What is my helplessness?
How do I tell you about that?"

02:34:42.473 --> 02:34:45.098
"Oh my beloved!"

02:34:45.359 --> 02:34:48.275
"Oh my beloved!"

02:34:48.478 --> 02:34:51.478
"Oh my beloved!"

02:34:51.559 --> 02:34:55.600
"Oh my beloved!"

02:34:57.028 --> 02:35:00.195
Raja, look at
your pathetic condition.

02:35:00.403 --> 02:35:03.195
Why are you ruining yourself
for that disloyal woman?

02:35:03.557 --> 02:35:04.641
Leave me alone, Daddy.

02:35:04.778 --> 02:35:07.111
How do I leave you alone?
I am your father after all.

02:35:07.570 --> 02:35:08.564
Come with me.

02:35:08.820 --> 02:35:10.861
We will teach such a lesson
to that girl and her father..

02:35:10.945 --> 02:35:12.486
..that they will remember
it throughout their lives.

02:35:12.736 --> 02:35:14.278
I will get you married
very pompously.

02:35:14.403 --> 02:35:16.739
Your wedding procession will pass
from the front of that girl's house.

02:35:16.820 --> 02:35:17.952
You'll see.

02:35:18.695 --> 02:35:21.878
Whether it is my funeral
or wedding procession..

02:35:22.776 --> 02:35:24.193
..doesn't make any difference to me.

02:35:25.278 --> 02:35:26.986
You are free to do whatever you want.

02:35:32.903 --> 02:35:35.070
Look, read it yourself.

02:35:35.736 --> 02:35:39.070
The person for whom you
cry day and night, your Raja..

02:35:39.361 --> 02:35:40.778
..is going to get married once again.

02:35:46.486 --> 02:35:47.986
Shakti! What happened?

02:35:51.153 --> 02:35:52.633
He has shown his true colours.

02:35:58.986 --> 02:36:00.003
Madhu..

02:36:02.820 --> 02:36:05.570
..for how long will
you live this way?

02:36:06.611 --> 02:36:09.195
I am unable to bear
this condition of yours.

02:36:09.914 --> 02:36:12.164
Child, your entire
life is ahead of you.

02:36:12.927 --> 02:36:14.386
Forget whatever has happened.

02:36:16.153 --> 02:36:17.581
Start life afresh.

02:36:19.653 --> 02:36:21.070
Get married to Shakti.

02:36:21.528 --> 02:36:22.736
No, Daddy.

02:36:23.361 --> 02:36:25.653
Never ever say it again.

02:36:26.486 --> 02:36:28.195
Leave me to my condition.

02:36:28.987 --> 02:36:29.814
Dear!

02:36:31.778 --> 02:36:34.028
How can I leave you in this state?

02:36:34.236 --> 02:36:35.736
I'm your father.

02:36:35.861 --> 02:36:37.653
I want your happiness.

02:36:39.153 --> 02:36:40.903
You want to see me happy, right?

02:36:41.028 --> 02:36:41.878
Yes.

02:36:42.945 --> 02:36:45.820
Then please take
me away from this place.

02:36:49.736 --> 02:36:55.236
Yes, dear. I'll take you.

02:36:56.462 --> 02:36:57.587
I'll take you far away.

02:36:58.028 --> 02:36:59.101
The auspicious time of
the engagement is passing by.

02:36:59.182 --> 02:37:00.611
Your son hasn't come until now.

02:37:00.854 --> 02:37:02.396
Raja might be on his way.

02:37:02.528 --> 02:37:05.236
But you have done all
the arrangements, isn't it?

02:37:05.486 --> 02:37:07.820
You need not worry at all,
Hazari Prasad.

02:37:08.195 --> 02:37:09.653
I have done all the arrangements.

02:37:09.810 --> 02:37:11.477
I remember my promise very well.

02:37:11.695 --> 02:37:12.535
Radhe Shyam!

02:37:24.695 --> 02:37:25.861
Thank you. Thank you.

02:37:26.111 --> 02:37:27.695
This is nothing at all,
Hazari Prasad.

02:37:27.820 --> 02:37:30.320
These are the gifts for the groom.
It is not the actual dowry.

02:37:30.613 --> 02:37:32.197
Let the marriage take place once.

02:37:32.278 --> 02:37:33.861
You will see that
you will not find place in...

02:37:33.945 --> 02:37:34.820
...your house to keep
all these things.

02:37:34.903 --> 02:37:36.403
For now I'll go and
find a place to keep this.

02:37:36.528 --> 02:37:38.153
Excuse me. Thank you. Thank you.

02:37:38.278 --> 02:37:42.111
I will keep so much money with me.
Oh my Goddess!

02:37:42.195 --> 02:37:43.290
Oh my Goddess!
- Listen,

02:37:44.027 --> 02:37:45.908
what are you doing for money?

02:37:46.236 --> 02:37:48.611
You are getting my
Raja married to a mad girl.

02:37:48.695 --> 02:37:50.778
All the girls are basically mad.
Look at yourself.

02:37:50.945 --> 02:37:53.028
If you were not mad then would
you say such unfortunate things..

02:37:53.111 --> 02:37:54.445
..on the occasion
of your son's engagement?

02:37:54.528 --> 02:37:57.403
Do you know what my son
is going through right now?

02:37:57.695 --> 02:38:00.153
He is heart broken.

02:38:00.695 --> 02:38:02.236
He has started drinking liquor.

02:38:02.361 --> 02:38:05.736
Do you know, he has not
come back home since last night.

02:38:05.945 --> 02:38:07.403
But you are not at
all bothered about him.

02:38:07.861 --> 02:38:09.486
Have mercy on your child!

02:38:09.695 --> 02:38:12.153
Don't be so cruel to him!
- Stop your rubbish!

02:38:12.320 --> 02:38:13.861
I know what I am doing. Okay?

02:38:18.111 --> 02:38:21.153
Last time when I wanted
to sell this coat, Mr. Pasricha.

02:38:21.570 --> 02:38:23.153
I thought that..

02:38:23.234 --> 02:38:24.984
Who is Mr.
Hazari Prasad amongst you all?

02:38:26.445 --> 02:38:28.236
It's me. What is the matter?

02:38:28.422 --> 02:38:30.047
Is this the photograph of your son?

02:38:30.653 --> 02:38:32.445
Yes. This is my son
Raja's photograph.

02:38:33.070 --> 02:38:34.153
What's the matter, Inspector?

02:38:34.236 --> 02:38:36.028
What has happened to him?
Is he all right?

02:38:36.153 --> 02:38:37.445
Your son has met with an accident.

02:38:37.570 --> 02:38:40.070
We have recovered all these
things from his dead body. - No!

02:38:40.198 --> 02:38:41.739
This is a lie! A lie!

02:38:41.820 --> 02:38:44.944
Then you confirm it yourself.
Constable, bring the body inside.

02:39:06.403 --> 02:39:07.789
No!

02:39:09.839 --> 02:39:11.214
My Raja!

02:39:13.278 --> 02:39:14.570
Raja!

02:39:15.320 --> 02:39:17.528
My son Raja!

02:39:25.111 --> 02:39:28.153
Now be assured! Be assured!

02:39:28.545 --> 02:39:30.629
You killer! You sinner!

02:39:31.233 --> 02:39:33.441
You have killed my son.

02:39:34.195 --> 02:39:37.073
You have separated Raja and Madhu.

02:39:37.154 --> 02:39:39.987
You have ruined all their happiness.

02:39:40.653 --> 02:39:46.486
When my son was fighting against
life and death in the hospital..

02:39:46.602 --> 02:39:49.518
..then instead of
saving you son's life..

02:39:49.778 --> 02:39:53.945
..you made a deal with
Madhu regarding her husband.

02:39:54.153 --> 02:39:56.051
You took away her husband from her.

02:39:56.132 --> 02:40:01.840
This is her curse which has
separated my son from me today.

02:40:02.639 --> 02:40:07.472
Now sell this corpse
also in the market.

02:40:07.695 --> 02:40:10.736
Maybe you will get
some money with that also.

02:40:10.820 --> 02:40:16.096
You have killed him.
Now sell him off. Sell him of.

02:40:17.865 --> 02:40:18.865
My son!

02:40:19.107 --> 02:40:20.055
Mother!

02:40:27.945 --> 02:40:31.115
My son, Raja! Raja!

02:40:31.195 --> 02:40:34.822
You are alive, my son?

02:40:34.903 --> 02:40:36.111
Yes, Mother.

02:40:37.653 --> 02:40:40.236
My Raja is alive.

02:40:41.418 --> 02:40:43.792
My son is alive.

02:40:46.656 --> 02:40:47.778
He is alive.

02:40:48.192 --> 02:40:51.150
Mr. Raja, how did your
clothes come on this corpse?

02:40:53.923 --> 02:40:55.881
I had drunk and I was
lying unconscious.

02:40:57.516 --> 02:41:00.557
At that time, he must have
stolen my coat and my chain.

02:41:00.903 --> 02:41:03.070
Then he must have
met with an accident.

02:41:05.611 --> 02:41:06.945
I wish that I had
died instead of him.

02:41:07.026 --> 02:41:09.484
No, Son. You should never say that.
- Don't touch me!

02:41:10.278 --> 02:41:13.028
But, son.. - Dare if you will call
me a son. Or even if you will touch me.

02:41:13.165 --> 02:41:16.332
But son, I have done all this for you.
- Not for me, Mr. Hazari Prasad.

02:41:17.445 --> 02:41:20.861
What am I to you?
Just a saleable thing.

02:41:22.361 --> 02:41:24.903
Besides selling me,
what else can you do?

02:41:26.653 --> 02:41:28.778
Maybe you had given birth
to me for this reason only.

02:41:30.203 --> 02:41:33.828
As a butcher nurtures
and nourishes a goat.

02:41:34.653 --> 02:41:36.611
Then he sells off every piece of his.

02:41:38.278 --> 02:41:40.570
No, Raja.
No! You are under a misunderstanding.

02:41:40.695 --> 02:41:42.073
You are telling lies.

02:41:44.236 --> 02:41:45.695
I have heard everything.

02:41:45.986 --> 02:41:48.528
I heard what you did with Madhu.
What sacrifice you asked her to make?

02:41:50.278 --> 02:41:51.861
Madhu was a stranger.

02:41:53.153 --> 02:41:56.570
But still for the sake of
my life she sacrificed her husband.

02:41:58.675 --> 02:42:02.508
But you. I was your very own blood.

02:42:03.653 --> 02:42:05.028
A part of you.

02:42:06.695 --> 02:42:09.653
Sometimes a hungry lion eats
his own children out of helplessness.

02:42:10.347 --> 02:42:12.972
But what was your helplessness, Mr.
Hazari Prasad?

02:42:13.512 --> 02:42:15.947
What were you hungry for?
How much hungry were you that..

02:42:16.028 --> 02:42:17.445
...didn't get satisfied even
after eating your own child?

02:42:17.550 --> 02:42:19.008
Stop it, child! Stop it!

02:42:19.528 --> 02:42:21.986
What are you crying for, Mr.
Hazari Prasad?

02:42:22.736 --> 02:42:26.195
You had said a few days
ago that you don't have any son.

02:42:26.843 --> 02:42:28.301
That I am not your son.

02:42:28.865 --> 02:42:31.365
Today I admit this in
front of all these people..

02:42:32.070 --> 02:42:35.278
..that after today,
you are not my father.

02:42:44.153 --> 02:42:47.486
Raja!
- Raja, my son, where are you going?

02:42:49.028 --> 02:42:51.570
I am going away from this
suffocation and embarrassment.

02:42:52.070 --> 02:42:53.653
I am going back to my Madhu.

02:43:00.320 --> 02:43:02.736
Take care of the house.
- Yes, Mother.

02:43:40.403 --> 02:43:42.861
Where are you going?
There's no one inside. - What?

02:43:43.278 --> 02:43:44.820
Where did everybody go?
- To the airport.

02:43:44.945 --> 02:43:48.153
Everyone is going to London
forever by the 4 o'clock flight.

02:44:43.861 --> 02:44:45.861
Hello. Haji Ali traffic control.

02:44:45.945 --> 02:44:48.111
A boy riding a red bike has
jumped the signal and is running away.

02:44:48.195 --> 02:44:49.653
Get hold of him immediately. Over!

02:44:49.778 --> 02:44:51.145
Received the message. Over and out!

02:45:14.195 --> 02:45:15.436
Are you riding the bike
under the influence of alcohol?

02:45:15.570 --> 02:45:16.695
Sir, I am really in
a hurry right now.

02:45:16.778 --> 02:45:17.858
I have to reach
the airport immediately.

02:45:18.028 --> 02:45:19.153
Show me the licence.

02:45:20.403 --> 02:45:21.695
Sir, the licence is at home.

02:45:21.903 --> 02:45:23.183
You must have papers
for the bike at least.

02:45:23.320 --> 02:45:25.486
Sir, please let me go.
I am in a real hurry.

02:45:25.861 --> 02:45:27.736
Have you stolen this bike?
- No, sir.

02:45:27.820 --> 02:45:29.611
Sir, I think that there is
something fishy here. - No, sir.

02:45:29.695 --> 02:45:31.736
Fine. Arrest him.
- Sir, please try to understand.

02:45:31.820 --> 02:45:33.611
Sir, trust me. Right now it
is the question of my life and death.

02:45:33.692 --> 02:45:35.892
I said, shut up. Come with me. Come.

02:45:37.278 --> 02:45:40.236
What is this nonsense?
Why did you catch his hand?

02:45:40.486 --> 02:45:42.486
Don't you know that I am with him?

02:45:42.820 --> 02:45:45.073
Why are you tormenting
my friend who is also a lover?

02:45:45.153 --> 02:45:47.611
Sir, please help me, sir.
If I don't reach the airport on time..

02:45:47.736 --> 02:45:49.316
..then my Madhu will
be separated from me forever.

02:45:49.445 --> 02:45:50.820
What are you saying?
- Yes. - Sir.

02:45:51.195 --> 02:45:52.820
He was breaking all the traffic
rules and running away. - No, sir.

02:45:52.945 --> 02:45:53.986
I guess, it is a matter of theft.

02:45:54.111 --> 02:45:56.153
Hey! It is not a matter of theft.

02:45:56.236 --> 02:45:57.570
It is a matter of a love affair.

02:45:57.767 --> 02:46:01.405
Hey! When the public
is crazy in love..

02:46:01.486 --> 02:46:03.820
..then our law will
not be able to do anything.

02:46:04.278 --> 02:46:06.419
I got it, sir.
- You got it, right?

02:46:06.570 --> 02:46:08.886
Now no plane will take
off from the airport until.

02:46:09.044 --> 02:46:11.544
I do not drop you at the airport.

02:46:11.861 --> 02:46:13.476
I will drop you there. Come on.
- Thank you, sir.

02:47:02.903 --> 02:47:07.320
Air India AI 111 is
ready to take off to London.

02:47:07.445 --> 02:47:11.820
The passengers are requested
to proceed to gate number 10.

02:47:54.111 --> 02:47:55.111
Excuse me, sir.
- Yes.

02:47:55.278 --> 02:47:56.528
The Air India flight,
which was supposed to fly to London.

02:47:56.611 --> 02:47:57.788
Sorry, sir.
The flight has already taken off.

02:48:31.320 --> 02:48:34.734
Please forgive me, son.

02:48:53.653 --> 02:48:56.403
Take this and put it around her neck.

02:49:24.361 --> 02:49:25.607
Just a minute. Just a minute.

02:49:25.688 --> 02:49:27.980
At least allow Dev
Anand to click a picture.

02:49:28.195 --> 02:49:31.403
Just a minute. Just a minute.
- Even you can join in, sir.

02:49:36.486 --> 02:49:37.957
I thought that..

02:49:39.528 --> 02:49:42.070
Brothers look, he the same
person who had given us fake money.

02:49:42.280 --> 02:49:44.405
I will hit him badly. Come on.

02:49:44.486 --> 02:49:46.694
Let's go. Come on. Get hold of him.

02:49:46.775 --> 02:49:48.442
You had distributed
fake currency amongst us.

02:49:48.695 --> 02:49:49.778
We will not spare you.

02:49:49.861 --> 02:49:51.278
Hey! Wait a minute. Wait a minute.

02:49:51.361 --> 02:49:52.903
This Hazari Prasad has changed now.

02:49:53.028 --> 02:49:54.278
This is not the old
Hazari Prasad now.

02:49:54.361 --> 02:49:56.278
Now look,
I will give you these notes.

02:49:56.359 --> 02:49:58.651
But daddy, these are fake ones.
- Hey! What are you saying?

02:49:58.778 --> 02:50:00.903
Fake and real..
Never mind! Never mind!

02:50:01.017 --> 02:50:02.447
But these are the real ones.

02:50:02.528 --> 02:50:06.111
"No one can match up to you."

02:50:07.312 --> 02:50:10.208
"I can't sleep. I have no solace."

02:50:10.289 --> 02:50:12.623
"Somebody,
please go and search for me."

02:50:12.715 --> 02:50:15.631
"I don't know where
my heart is lost."

02:50:15.750 --> 02:50:18.758
"I don't know where
my heart is lost."
